def post(href img datetime date cathref cat title avatar author role)
  article group flex flex-col items-start
    a(href={href}) relative w-full overflow-hidden rounded-2xl
      img(src={img} alt="") aspect-[16/9] w-full bg-slate-200 object-cover transition duration-300 group-hover:scale-105
      . absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl ring-1 ring-inset ring-slate-900/10
    . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs
      time(datetime={datetime}) text-slate-500 "{date}"
      a(href={cathref}) rounded-full bg-slate-100 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200 "{cat}"
    h3 mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-900 group-hover:text-emerald-700 > a(href={href}) "{title}"
    p mt-3 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600
      children
    . mt-6 flex items-center gap-x-3
      img(src={avatar} alt="") h-9 w-9 rounded-full bg-slate-200 object-cover
      . text-sm leading-5
        p font-semibold text-slate-900 "{author}"
        p text-slate-600 "{role}"

section bg-slate-50 py-24 sm:py-32 > . mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8
  . mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0
    h2 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl "From the Fieldnotes blog"
    p mt-2 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600
      | Engineering deep dives, launch stories, and hard-won lessons from building agricultural sensing at scale.
  . mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3
    +post(href="/blog/soil-probe-v3" img="/img/blog/soil-probe-field.jpg" datetime="2026-06-18" date="Jun 18, 2026" cathref="/blog/category/hardware" cat="Hardware" title="Designing a soil probe that survives five winters underground" avatar="/img/team/anna.jpg" author="Anna Delgado" role="Head of Hardware")
      | Frost heave destroyed 30% of our v2 probes in the first season. Here's how a redesigned housing, a new potting compound, and one counterintuitive antenna decision got failures under 1%.
    +post(href="/blog/lora-mesh-lessons" img="/img/blog/lora-gateway.jpg" datetime="2026-05-30" date="May 30, 2026" cathref="/blog/category/engineering" cat="Engineering" title="What 40,000 LoRa nodes taught us about mesh networking" avatar="/img/team/tomas.jpg" author="Tomas Novak" role="Staff Firmware Engineer")
      | Textbook mesh routing collapses when half your nodes sleep 99% of the time. We walk through the scheduling protocol that cut packet loss from 12% to 0.4% across our largest deployment.
    +post(href="/blog/irrigation-savings-study" img="/img/blog/pivot-irrigation.jpg" datetime="2026-05-12" date="May 12, 2026" cathref="/blog/category/research" cat="Research" title="Two seasons of data: sensor-driven irrigation cut water use 31%" avatar="/img/team/grace.jpg" author="Grace Okafor" role="Agronomy Research Lead")
      | Results from our study with 14 Nebraska corn growers, including the full methodology, the fields where it didn't work, and what that means for scheduling models.
